Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:35.31,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}悲しみにも負けない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.00,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}勇気だけをください
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:44.25,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}大切なもの  守るため
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:49.66,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}「強さ」はあると信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:55.52,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Saving our future　一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.68,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}明日へのドア開いた空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.14,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}飛び立とう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:07.00,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}とある世界の果てで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:12.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}駆け抜けてく　Real Force
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:20.38,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}光を放って!
