Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:04.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:08.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:36.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千鈞一髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:39.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:41.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:43.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所幸的是沒有人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  為了防止恐慌散佈開來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請準備好對外公佈的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  實際上這不是地震…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是雜亂開放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是雜亂開放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:38.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:42.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您救了我們的朋友  我們實在不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人受傷實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:51.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對這裏存在的AIM擴散力場進行檢查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MAR能夠事先探測到力場的異常嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對應得實在太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:09.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是風紀委員第177支部的白井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:09.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(265,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:14.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在177支部裏  好像聚集了很多優秀的人才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:20.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連RSPK和AIM擴散力場的關係都已經掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:27.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RSPK的原因是不知來自何方的對AIM擴散力場的人為干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:31.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時在多處發生就會發生雜亂開放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:31.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若能在協同會議裏說明的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:39.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員也能協助進行對可疑人物的分辨的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:39.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(160,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面由警備員管轄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如會議當中說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望風紀委員能夠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:48.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心負責好應付對外界不良評價的影響和日常安全措施哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對AIM擴散力場的干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:55.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到這種事情的人還有其他人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要陪她去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經快到舍監巡視的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  這我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:13.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:18.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學  好像已經平安回到宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始在調查些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想御手事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今怎麼還…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:37.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得跟這次的雜亂開放事件有點相似
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:37.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:41.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  那終究是利用AIM擴散力場的犯罪對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:42.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我也會不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是看不慣的話  屆時歡迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事件是否也跟木山有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了最關鍵的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:06.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山春生現在被拘留在17學區的特別監獄裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:10.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那樣的重犯沒那麼容易出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事黑子很在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:16.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那時的春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:20.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在與不在場的誰說話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的雜亂開放事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是AIM擴散力場的人為干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:41.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  應該是能力者所為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:45.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我也不想這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  這怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學才剛剛轉學過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  春上同學的19學區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雜亂開放事件的多發區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學是這樣說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:07.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第19學區在最近好像沒有發生雜亂開放事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:07.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其相對的卻在這個第7學區裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是偶然啦偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那樣那麼老實的孩子怎麼可能跟雜亂開放有關嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:21.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說實不應該那麼多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為固法學姐的電話完全忘…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固法學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然沒事也得聯絡我告訴我沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  你老是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真甜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你特意陪同實在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的室友  也就是我的摯友候選
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:58.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得今天老讓佐天同學幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來還真讓我們嚇一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對地震的時候的事情什麼都想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:09.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按醫院的醫生所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是受到了輕度打擊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:18.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然變成了很不得了的煙花晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒事真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要好好照顧春上同學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:30.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:44.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍里的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎麼樣  要喝點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:57.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  我給大家添麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:00.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:08.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會讓大家討厭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:09.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:13.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  春上同學有我跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:18.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學來探望你的時候帶來了好東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:29.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:32.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是熊本產的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學說  吃學園都市栽培的沒有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學也是佐天同學也是…大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我一個人什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這等待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼討厭這樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:53.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  一定會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:01.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧大家才能當上風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學也是  有大家在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:09.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會…改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然  我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  吃個夠打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然公園？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟春上同學兩個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾  為什麼不叫上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來根本沒聽你說今天不用執勤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  偶然這樣呼吸一下…外面的空氣也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說是不是吸過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘氣喘得很厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回事…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:55.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  難得來玩  居然被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不是隨便來玩的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  要我買點什麼冰凍的東西來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:10.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就中華冷面跟五目炒飯和炸蝦和沙拉烏冬跟還有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春卷也不錯呢  甜的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}那個…要點到什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是很讓人在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:19.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:24.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  為了排除對春上同學的懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:24.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:25.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:31.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…能力是精神感應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Telepathy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神感應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:41.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是異能力也就是說基本還未能實際應用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:41.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學跟亂雜開放無關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只是我們多慮了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:48.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:50.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\i1}在特定波長的情況下{\i0}\N{\i1}可能有發揮出高於級別的能力的例外{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風吹得真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:12.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個時候吃的壽司卷為什麼那麼好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在之前的那個晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學所說的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:25.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想  「一定能夠改變」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:37.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要跟初春同學坦白說才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:39.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找一位朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:45.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前一直很要好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:47.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:51.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在某一天就分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能再次相見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我等待著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  光是等待是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若不自己去尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使現在這一刻…她也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  讓我們一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:18.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏…到底在哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會那麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:35.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:53.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:57.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}真沒想到會那麼好吃  再去買一些吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第21學區的自然公園…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生大規模的亂雜開放？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然公園…不就是初春她們所在的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷亡情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:39.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷者72名  其中重傷者18名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還沒有人員死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續進行救援工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:44.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這確實與真正的地震沒什麼區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  你也一起過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的  我是風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(385,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏還有我力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是上次的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特蕾斯蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:07.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  害你們特意趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:17.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過受了點擦傷罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就說過這點傷不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可擔心死我們了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:28.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  竟然會接二連三地遇上亂雜開放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:28.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和春上同學也真夠不走運的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  春上同學上哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她之前就被送走了  大概就在附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的  她沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼  不過沒受傷真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:45.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂雜開放發生前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學有沒有表現出什麼異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如像上次煙火大會時那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你到底在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我調查  春上同學雖然是異能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是個有些不同尋常的精神感應者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:06.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若她再有像上次那樣不可思議的行為的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:07.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要去調查那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:12.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說白井同學在懷疑春上同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了  白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學她才剛轉校過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她感到不安  並十分依賴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你卻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點啦  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:35.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  初春同學  黑子她不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:40.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能排除精神感應者就是AIM力場的干涉者的可能性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:40.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(215,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裏已經人滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的人就送去第15學區的緊急醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:50.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:51.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:56.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那需要是大能力者以上等級的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:56.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的人可說是少之又少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:03.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得憑一個異能力者是幾乎不可能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:03.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為了保險起見  還是進行些檢查比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的朋友的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上衿衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:11.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一名受災人員  請送往本部的研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調一輛車到門口來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:16.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是為了還她一個清白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:23.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我們那裏有很多專業的工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  在醫院請保持安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就拿西瓜紅茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我嗓子都快冒煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  黑子你也喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  春上同學她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:05.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌  等結果出來還需要一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:22.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏完全看不出是個研究所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是審美很特別還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個女人卻在從事災難救援方面的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難讓人相信我會喜歡這些純粹的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  是我的愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:44.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  讓我重新自我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:48.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是先進狀況救助隊附屬研究所所長——特裏斯蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所長？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:55.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…同時兼任MAR的隊長  以及研究所的所長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…還有什麼職務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:04.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來  我還不知道白井同學之外的人的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:05.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫御阪美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就是常盤台的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能在這裏遇到那位超電磁炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:14.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:15.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:16.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫佐天淚子  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是常盤台的學生麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是柵川中學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是御阪同學的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明你也是一名相當厲害的能力者嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必說了  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:35.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:39.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是風紀委員第177支部的初春飾利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:39.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(246,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那你和白井同學是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:41.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:45.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學她不是干涉者…不是犯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:55.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都喜歡  硬要說的話就是黃色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是黃色了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這到底是幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是個好兆頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:07.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:15.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們  知道本小姐是常盤台中學的婚後光子還這麼失禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都說了很多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為發生在大能力者等級身上的亂雜開放現象十分罕見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Poltergeist
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:22.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你再配合進行些檢查…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的身體狀況可是好得不得了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾卡瑟琳娜可是一直都在等著我回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學  御阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快攔住她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:49.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:51.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:55.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:01.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  她不是干涉者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她是個異能力者等級的精神感應者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只能接受感應
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能主動發送信念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根據書庫中記載的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:16.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在特定的波長作用下  是能夠破例發揮出原有等級以上的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學  你還在說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅根據檢查結果來看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個現象的對象是被限定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:27.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有是與那個對象之間才能夠無視距離及障礙物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確地接收到那種波長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:34.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  她是不可能成為AIM擴散力場干涉者的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  我就說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  倘若真是如此的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的干涉者到底是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:52.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:06.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你最重要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這包含著我和朋友間的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的朋友就是你正在尋找的那個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠聽到她的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是精神感應者麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Telepath
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是偶然能聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  一聽到她的聲音  我的腦海就一片空白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  那個時候也是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏面裝了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫枝先絆理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:45.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:49.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識她嗎
